3.   ISSUES FOR DISCUSSION
 
WG21 requests that SC22 accept our revised schedule and target dates.
 
The three-year term of WG21's convener, Sam Harbison, expires at the
1996 SC22 plenary meeting, and Dr. Harbison regrets that he will be
unable to serve for another three-year term. WG21 expects the United
States to propose Tom Plum as the new convener, and WG21 supports that
proposal.
 
